/**
 * Set the history service for logging dispatched notifications.
 *
 * When set, every dispatched notification is logged to the history
 * service after delivery (or delivery failure). If no history service
 * is set, notifications are still dispatched normally but not logged
 * to the persistent history (backward-compatible behavior).
 *
 * @param historyService - The history service to use, or null to disable.
 */
